    WHERE ([x0].[GebruikerId] = @__bestelling_GebruikerId_0) AND (CONVERT(date, [x0].[Bezorgdatum]) = @__bestelling_Bezorgdatum_Date_1)

) AS [t] ON [x.ProductenPerBestellingen].[BestellingId] = [t].[BestellingId]
ORDER BY [t].[BestellingId]"
